Package com.github.thesmartenergy.sparql.generate.jena.iterator Description

Contains the model for SPARQL Generate iterator functions. SPARQL Generate iterator functions are similar to SPARQL functions, except they return a list of RDF terms or SPARQL variables, instead of only one.
